data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Bardstown, Kentucky! This inviting residence offers three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, providing ample space for both relaxation and functionality. One of the standout features of this property is the expansive fenced-in rear yard, providing a secure and private oasis for outdoor activities and entertaining. Whether you're enjoying a quiet morning coffee on the patio or hosting a summer barbecue. Additionally, a convenient storage shed in the rear yard offers practical solutions for organizing and storing your belongings, ensuring a clutter-free living environment. Refrigerator, oven, range, dishwasher, washer/dryer to remain with the home in as is condition. Don't miss the chance to own this delightful property in Bardstown, Kentucky!
